g.text: Explaination: After the first flashing (bootloader to 0x08000000, Backup Application to 0x08002000, Application (*) to 0x08004000, counter = 0, run MCU.Bootloader run, now counter = 1 -> jump to 0x08004000 (now is Application (*)) -> reset and run Bootloader again, now counter = 2 -> erase Application (*) in 0x08004000 then write Backup Application aka Application (**) to 0x08004000-> jump to 0x08004000 (now is Application (**)) -> run Application (**)
